<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 18:09:07 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>其基布兹宣布，56 岁以色列人自 10 月 7 日起失踪，被宣告死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/56-year-old-israeli-thought-missing-since-october-7-declared-dead-his-kibbutz-announces/0000018c-c5be-d6c4-ab8d-e5bec2a10000</link><description>伊兰·韦斯 (Ilan Weiss) 的妻子和女儿希里·韦斯 (Shiri Weiss) 和诺加·韦斯 (Noga Weiss) 从贝埃里 (Be&amp;#39;eri) 被绑架到加沙，并于 11 月 26 日作为与哈马斯人质交易的一部分获释</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 16:22:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/56-year-old-israeli-thought-missing-since-october-7-declared-dead-his-kibbutz-announces/0000018c-c5be-d6c4-ab8d-e5bec2a10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列高等法院驳回内塔尼亚胡政府司法政变法限制其权力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/israels-high-court-set-to-release-ruling-on-netanyahu-govt-key-judicial-coup-law/0000018c-c01f-d3e0-abac-d8bf3c2d0000</link><description>15 名法官中有 8 名裁定该修正案无效，该修正案据称取消了法院推翻不合理政府决定的权力。 15项中的12项裁定最高法院有权对基本法进行司法审查</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 16:16:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/israels-high-court-set-to-release-ruling-on-netanyahu-govt-key-judicial-coup-law/0000018c-c01f-d3e0-abac-d8bf3c2d0000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日，一名坦桑尼亚父亲前往以色列寻找儿子被杀的答案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-tanzanian-father-journeys-to-israel-to-seek-answers-for-his-sons-killing-on-oct-7/0000018c-c516-d4e1-ad8f-fdb7243a0000</link><description>坦桑尼亚学生约书亚·莫勒尔在抵达以色列基布兹学习农业几周后，在哈马斯的袭击中被谋杀。两个月来，他的父亲一直希望儿子能回到他身边——直到一段记录他被谋杀的视频开始在社交媒体上流传</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 15:48:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-tanzanian-father-journeys-to-israel-to-seek-answers-for-his-sons-killing-on-oct-7/0000018c-c516-d4e1-ad8f-fdb7243a0000</guid></item><item><title>由于对加沙战争的预算担忧，以色列政府质疑情报部的必要性</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/amid-budget-concerns-over-war-israeli-govt-question-need-for-intelligence-ministry/0000018c-c56c-d4e1-ad8f-fdfd253f0000</link><description>虽然该部的任务是协调以色列各个情报机构之间的关系，但这些机构并不在该部之下运作。这是财政部因效率问题建议关闭的十个办事处之一</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 15:27:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/amid-budget-concerns-over-war-israeli-govt-question-need-for-intelligence-ministry/0000018c-c56c-d4e1-ad8f-fdfd253f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列外长敦促任命内塔尼亚胡的私人医生和心腹为名誉领事</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/israeli-fm-pushed-to-appoint-netanyahus-personal-physician-an-honorary-consul/0000018c-c467-d6c4-ab8d-e5f7ff3a0000</link><description>外交部长伊莱·科恩“向我保证这将会发生”，兹维·伯科维茨博士说，他的任命是在部长的一次不同寻常的干预后获得批准的。他被认为是内塔尼亚胡夫妇最亲密的知己</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 14:57:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/israeli-fm-pushed-to-appoint-netanyahus-personal-physician-an-honorary-consul/0000018c-c467-d6c4-ab8d-e5f7ff3a0000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦活动家将在未经审判的情况下被关押四个月——他在脸书上发帖称不是他的</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-activist-held-without-trial-for-4-months-for-facebook-posts-he-says-arent-his/0000018c-c4c7-ddba-abad-c6e70cbd0000</link><description>律师告诉《国土报》，自战争开始以来，许多巴勒斯坦人未经审判就被关押，因为这些指控通常不会导致达成这一协议；以色列国防军表示正在“调查”家人在逮捕期间遭受暴力的指控</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 12:28:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-activist-held-without-trial-for-4-months-for-facebook-posts-he-says-arent-his/0000018c-c4c7-ddba-abad-c6e70cbd0000</guid></item><item><title>英特尔的巨额投资对以色列来说是福音——但现在庆祝可能还为时过早</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/intels-huge-investment-is-a-boon-for-israel-but-it-might-be-too-soon-to-celebrate/0000018c-b047-d45c-a98e-bb4f3f6f0000</link><description>英特尔宣布在以色列南部建设新工厂是一次重大的信心表现。但该公司敏感的战略和业务地位，以及执行过去交易的延迟，增加了潜在的风险</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 12:04:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/intels-huge-investment-is-a-boon-for-israel-but-it-might-be-too-soon-to-celebrate/0000018c-b047-d45c-a98e-bb4f3f6f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的炸弹正在摧毁加沙的整个巴勒斯坦家庭</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-01-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israels-bombs-are-wiping-out-entire-palestinian-families-in-gaza/0000018c-c081-d3e0-abac-d8a9d4300000</link><description>大约 1,800 个加沙家庭在战争中失去了许多成员。正如一位研究人员所说，“过去的社会和家庭支持——无论是物质的、情感的还是象征性的——现在几乎不存在了。人们主要处于生存模式”</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 11:56:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-01-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israels-bombs-are-wiping-out-entire-palestinian-families-in-gaza/0000018c-c081-d3e0-abac-d8a9d4300000</guid></item><item><title>据报道，以色列男子因冒充士兵参加加沙战争而被指控与内塔尼亚胡合影</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/israeli-man-indicted-for-impersonating-soldier-reportedly-posed-in-photo-op-with-netanyahu/0000018c-c49a-d4e1-ad8f-fcbbd5200000</link><description>刑事指控称，该男子从未在以色列军队服役，但仍然通过假装是精锐作战部队的成员成功进入战区</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 11:19:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/israeli-man-indicted-for-impersonating-soldier-reportedly-posed-in-photo-op-with-netanyahu/0000018c-c49a-d4e1-ad8f-fcbbd5200000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡想让卡塔尔成为 10 月 7 日大屠杀的替罪羊。别让他</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-wants-to-make-qatar-the-fall-guy-for-october-7-massacre-dont-let-him/0000018c-c45d-dcff-adbf-cefff5250000</link><description>卡塔尔人多年来资助哈马斯，庇护其领导人，并将其合法化为一个政治力量。但它所做的一切都是在以色列完全同意和鼓励下完成的。现在，由于卡塔尔是中东政治中的一个“摇摆国家”，其批评者更好地承认它将在重新配置的地区中发挥关键作用</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 11:15:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-wants-to-make-qatar-the-fall-guy-for-october-7-massacre-dont-let-him/0000018c-c45d-dcff-adbf-cefff5250000</guid></item><item><title>“我喜欢你的加沙文章。这些腐朽人民的苦难和痛苦是我的燃料”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/i-enjoy-your-gaza-articles-the-suffering-and-pain-of-this-rotten-nation-is-my-fuel/0000018c-c482-ddba-abad-c6a377ba0000</link><description>杀戮、毁灭、痛苦：对于大多数以色列人来说，这是适当的惩罚</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 10:35:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/i-enjoy-your-gaza-articles-the-suffering-and-pain-of-this-rotten-nation-is-my-fuel/0000018c-c482-ddba-abad-c6a377ba0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的法律顾问抨击他参与延长警察局长任期，称其违反利益冲突</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-legal-adviser-slams-his-involvement-in-extending-police-chiefs-term/0000018c-c418-dcff-adbf-cefe146f0000</link><description>前以色列总检察长表示，以色列总理不得参与“参与针对总理的刑事诉讼”的国家机构高级官员的任命或选拔，因为内塔尼亚胡就警察局长的任期在部长之间进行调解</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 09:37:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-legal-adviser-slams-his-involvement-in-extending-police-chiefs-term/0000018c-c418-dcff-adbf-cefe146f0000</guid></item><item><title>在新星狂欢大屠杀中，自拍和录像是一种反抗行为</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/at-the-nova-rave-massacre-selfies-and-reels-were-an-act-of-defiance/0000018c-c092-d4e1-ad8f-fcb3d00d0000</link><description>10 月 7 日，以色列南部的 Supernova 音乐节上有超过 360 人被哈马斯杀害。纪录片“#Nova”揭露了当天的一些恐怖事件，这些恐怖分子和狂欢者都捕捉到了这些恐怖事件。这不是他们唯一的共同点</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 07:03:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/at-the-nova-rave-massacre-selfies-and-reels-were-an-act-of-defiance/0000018c-c092-d4e1-ad8f-fcb3d00d0000</guid></item><item><title>国家官员担心国际法院可能指控以色列在加沙犯有种族灭绝罪</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/state-officials-fear-hauge-could-charge-israel-with-genocide-in-gaza/0000018c-c1a9-d3e0-abac-d9a9acd80000</link><description>国际法院在制定国际法方面具有巨大影响力。国际法专家雪莉·阿维夫·耶尼 (Shelly Aviv Yeini) 博士表示，承认南非的主张可能会加深人们对以色列在加沙实施种族灭绝的看法。</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 04:52:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/state-officials-fear-hauge-could-charge-israel-with-genocide-in-gaza/0000018c-c1a9-d3e0-abac-d9a9acd80000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军士兵在加沙战斗中丧生；以色列极右翼部长呼吁永久控制加沙和定居点</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article-live/israel-brings-in-the-new-year-with-sirens-across-central-israel/0000018c-c318-d4e1-ad8f-ffb949720000</link><description>被认为自 10 月 7 日袭击以来失踪的以色列人被宣布死亡 ■ 以色列国防军击毙哈马斯精锐部队指挥官 ■ 以色列担心国际机场。法院对加沙战争提出指控 ■ 伊拉克军方消息人士称，无人机在伊拉克艾因阿萨德基地上空被拦截 ■ 自加沙地面行动开始以来，已有 30 名以色列士兵在事故和误伤中丧生。自10月7日以来，以色列至少有1,300名平民和士兵被杀；至少 133 名人质在加沙被扣押 ■ 哈马斯卫生部：加沙 21,822 人死亡，56,451 人受伤</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 04:14:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article-live/israel-brings-in-the-new-year-with-sirens-across-central-israel/0000018c-c318-d4e1-ad8f-ffb949720000</guid></item><item><title>与以色列的全面战争可能损害真主党的政治利益</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/full-blown-israel-war-could-harm-hezbollahs-political-interests/0000018c-c194-d6c4-ab8d-e1b4c2eb0000</link><description>该国颇具影响力的马龙派基督教权威表示，它不“希望战争蔓延到黎巴嫩南部”，鉴于真主党在政府中的地位，它必须表明它正在为黎巴嫩的国家利益而努力</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 04:01:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/full-blown-israel-war-could-harm-hezbollahs-political-interests/0000018c-c194-d6c4-ab8d-e1b4c2eb0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警探被控七月袭击反政府抗议者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-detective-charged-with-assaulting-anti-government-protester-in-july/0000018c-c180-d3e0-abac-d9a99deb0000</link><description>德克尔·拉齐米（Dekel Lazimi）殴打了一名被束缚且没有拒捕的抗议者。 《国土报》拍摄了这一事件。抗议者说：“我很清楚，如果没有记录下来，他们就不会相信我。”</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Dec 2023 23:47:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-detective-charged-with-assaulting-anti-government-protester-in-july/0000018c-c180-d3e0-abac-d9a99deb0000</guid></item><item><title>2023 年是以色列自 1950 年开始记录以来最热的年份之一</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/2023-was-one-of-israels-hottest-years-since-keeping-of-records-began-in-1950/0000018c-c181-d3e0-abac-d9a948f60000</link><description>根据以色列气象局的年度总结，2023年5月下旬和6月发生了四次异常降雨事件，7月和8月出现了持续且异常的热浪，11月和12月出现了异常大雨。</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Dec 2023 23:22:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-01/ty-article/.premium/2023-was-one-of-israels-hottest-years-since-keeping-of-records-began-in-1950/0000018c-c181-d3e0-abac-d9a948f60000</guid></item><item><title>2024 年前夕，反内塔尼亚胡抗议者对 10 月 7 日的事件感到愤怒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-12-31/ty-article/.highlight/on-the-eve-of-2024-anti-netanyahu-protesters-are-fueled-with-rage-over-october-7/0000018c-c08c-d6c4-ab8d-e1bc94de0000</link><description>虽然之前的司法政变抗议传递的信息是对未来潜在损害的警告，但现在由于内塔尼亚胡未能保护国家，已经付出了血腥的代价</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Dec 2023 19:49:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-12-31/ty-article/.highlight/on-the-eve-of-2024-anti-netanyahu-protesters-are-fueled-with-rage-over-october-7/0000018c-c08c-d6c4-ab8d-e1bc94de0000</guid></item><item><title>极端正统沙斯党推动法案推迟最高法院对司法政变法的裁决</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-31/ty-article/.premium/ultra-orthodox-shas-party-pushing-bill-to-delay-top-court-ruling-on-judicial-coup-law/0000018c-c148-d3e0-abac-d9e974ae0000</link><description>根据该法案，退休的最高法院法官将被允许在退休后九个月内公布剩余裁决，而不是像现在这样三个月</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Dec 2023 19:49:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-31/ty-article/.premium/ultra-orthodox-shas-party-pushing-bill-to-delay-top-court-ruling-on-judicial-coup-law/0000018c-c148-d3e0-abac-d9e974ae0000</guid></item></channel></rss>